HEADWORD: Arcograph
<hw>Arc"o*graph</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>arcus</ets> (E. <ets>arc</ets>) + <ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <def>An
